trans-unit.source: Implemented by the <xref href="System.EnterpriseServices.ServicedComponent"></xref> class to determine if the <xref href="System.EnterpriseServices.AutoCompleteAttribute"></xref> class attribute is set to <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> or <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> for a remote method invocation.
trans-unit.target: Implementert av den <xref href="System.EnterpriseServices.ServicedComponent"> </xref> klassen for å finne ut om den <xref href="System.EnterpriseServices.AutoCompleteAttribute"> </xref> klasseattributtet er satt til <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref> eller <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> for en ekstern metodeaktivering.

trans-unit.source: The IRemoteDispatch interface does not need to be implemented directly in your code.
trans-unit.target: Grensesnittet IRemoteDispatch trenger ikke å implementeres direkte i koden.

trans-unit.source: It is used internally by the .NET Framework infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Det er brukt internt av .NET Framework-infrastruktur.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.AutoCompleteAttribute> class attribute ensures that, in the COM+ context, the object's done bit is automatically set to `true` once the method returns.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.AutoCompleteAttribute>klasseattributtet sikrer at COM +-kontekst objektets ferdig bit er automatisk satt til `true` når returneres.</xref:System.EnterpriseServices.AutoCompleteAttribute>

trans-unit.source: The object can then be deactivated.
The IRemoteDispatch interface methods do not appear in the <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.ServicedComponent> class interface.
trans-unit.target: Metodene IRemoteDispatch grensesnittet vises ikke i den <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.ServicedComponent>grensesnittet klassen.</xref:System.EnterpriseServices.ServicedComponent>

trans-unit.source: Ensures that, in the COM+ context, the <xref href="System.EnterpriseServices.ServicedComponent"></xref> class object's done bit is set to <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> after a remote method invocation.
trans-unit.target: Sikrer at, i COM +-kontekst i <xref href="System.EnterpriseServices.ServicedComponent"> </xref> klassen objektets ferdig bit er satt til <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref> etter en ekstern metodeaktivering.

trans-unit.source: The RemoteDispatchAutoDone method does not belong to the published interface of the <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.ServicedComponent> class and does not need to be implemented elsewhere.
trans-unit.target: Metoden RemoteDispatchAutoDone tilhører ikke publisert grensesnittet for den <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.ServicedComponent>klasse og trenger ikke å implementeres andre steder.</xref:System.EnterpriseServices.ServicedComponent>

trans-unit.source: A string to be converted into a request object that implements the <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.Messaging.IMessage"></xref> interface.
trans-unit.target: En streng som skal konverteres til et objekt som implementerer den <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.Messaging.IMessage"> </xref> grensesnitt.

trans-unit.source: A string converted from a response object that implements the <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.Messaging.IMethodReturnMessage"></xref> interface.
trans-unit.target: En streng som er konvertert fra en svar-objekt som implementerer den <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.Messaging.IMethodReturnMessage"> </xref> grensesnitt.

trans-unit.source: Does not ensure that, in the COM+ context, the <xref href="System.EnterpriseServices.ServicedComponent"></xref> class object's done bit is set to <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> after a remote method invocation.
trans-unit.target: Sikrer som ikke i COM +-kontekst i <xref href="System.EnterpriseServices.ServicedComponent"> </xref> klassen objektets ferdig bit er satt til <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref> etter en ekstern metodeaktivering.

trans-unit.source: The RemoteDispatchNotAutoDone method does not belong to the published interface of the <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.ServicedComponent> class and does not need to be implemented elsewhere.
trans-unit.target: Metoden RemoteDispatchNotAutoDone tilhører ikke publisert grensesnittet for den <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.ServicedComponent>klasse og trenger ikke å implementeres andre steder.</xref:System.EnterpriseServices.ServicedComponent>

trans-unit.source: A string to be converted into a request object implementing the <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.Messaging.IMessage"></xref> interface.
trans-unit.target: En streng som skal konverteres til en forespørsel objektet implementering av <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.Messaging.IMessage"> </xref> grensesnitt.

trans-unit.source: A string converted from a response object implementing the <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.Messaging.IMethodReturnMessage"></xref> interface.
trans-unit.target: En streng konvertert fra en svar objektet implementering av <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.Messaging.IMethodReturnMessage"> </xref> grensesnitt.
